<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Comparos Mock Publisher Test Environment</title>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI", Inter, sans-serif;
      background-color: #0f111a;
      color: #e2e8f0;
      line-height: 1.6;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 40px 20px;
    }
    .wrapper {
      max-width: 900px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      background: #1a1d29;
      padding: 35px;
      border-radius: 8px;
      border: 1px solid #2d3142;
      box-shadow: 0 10px 25px rgba(0,0,0,0.3);
    }
    h1 { color: #fff; margin-top: 0; border-bottom: 1px solid #2d3142; padding-bottom: 15px; font-weight: 500; }
    code { background: #0f111a; padding: 3px 6px; border-radius: 4px; color: #a370f7; font-family: monospace; }
    
    /* Publisher Ad Placement Styling */
    .publisher-ad-zone {
      margin: 35px 0;
      padding: 12px;
      background: #0f111a;
      border: 1px dashed #4e546d;
      border-radius: 6px;
    }
    .ad-notice {
      font-size: 11px;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: 1.5px;
      color: #64748b;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
      text-align: center;
      font-weight: 600;
    }
    p { color: #94a3b8; font-size: 15px; }
  </style>
</head>
<body>

  <div class="wrapper">
    <h1>Mock Publisher Stage</h1>
    <p>This page simulates a live production article page layout. When it loads, your universal tag script calls the master architecture remotely from GitHub via the jsDelivr CDN cache grid.</p>
    
    <div class="publisher-ad-zone">
      <div class="ad-notice">Programmatic Video Advertisement Space</div>
      
      <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/aryanvani-pm/Player-engine@main/player.JS"
              id="adtech-player-core"
              data-pub-id="649658371"
              data-adunit-id="972556929"
              data-tag="https://pubads.g.doubleclick.net/gampad/ads?iu=/21775744923/external/single_ad_samples&sz=640x480&cust_params=sample_ct%3Dlinear&ciu_szs=300x250%2C728x90&gdfp_req=1&output=vast&unviewed_position_start=1&env=vp&impl=s&correlator="
              data-timeout="1200"
              data-bias="0.10"
              data-video="https://vjs.zencdn.net/v/oceans.mp4"
              data-autoplay="true"
              data-muted="true"
              data-fluid="true"
              data-loop="true"
              data-preload="metadata"
              data-vpaid="insecure"
              data-div-id="comparos-video-placement"
              data-host="ads-jbi003.rtba.bidsxchange.com"
              data-cache="https://prebid.adnxs.com/pbc/v1/cache"
              data-prebid-url="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/aryanvani-pm/Player-engine@main/prebid.js"
              async></script>
      </div>

    <p>All core infrastructure assets—including Video.js themes, Google IMA runtime loaders, and your standalone repo <code>prebid.js</code> library—are handled on the fly using non-blocking asynchronous promises.</p>
  </div>

</body>
</html>
